OL,6,FA suicidal patient was beaten and hit
OL,7,Fover the head 46 times by three
OL,8,Fsecurity guards in a 'shocking display
OL,9,Fof abuse of power' after being
OL,10,Fadmitted to hospital.
OL,12,FAfter the man was rushed to North
OL,13,FGeneral Hospital, medical staff called
OL,14,Fin four security guards because the
OL,15,Fvictim, who had taken an overdose,
OL,16,Fbecame 'difficult to manage'.
