OL,6,FBut over the course of an hour, three
OL,7,Fguards battered the vulnerable
OL,8,Fpatient, hitting him over the head 46
OL,9,Ftimes, slapping him, pulling his hair
OL,10,Fand locking him in painful restraint
OL,11,Fpositions, leaving the man covered in
OL,12,Fbruises.JSupervisor Abdul Saleem, 36,
OL,13,Ffrom Stretford, , and Darling Owa, 55,
OL,14,Ffrom Chadderton, , were brought before
OL,15,Fa judge after their own body-worn
OL,16,Fcameras filmed the assault on 25
OL,17,FJanuary 2023.
