OL,6,FThey both pleaded guilty to assaulting
OL,7,Fthe 43-year-old and have since lost
OL,8,Ftheir jobs at the hospital in
OL,9,FCrumpsall, but were spared being
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FA third guard, Benjamin Monese, 39,
OL,13,Ffrom Farnworth, , had been sentenced
OL,14,Fearlier. A fourth guard present was
OL,15,Fnot charged.JJudge Kate Cornell
OL,16,Fdescribed the episode as a 'shocking
OL,17,Fdisplay of abuse of power'. She said
OL,18,Fthe victim should have felt 'safe' at
OL,19,Fthe hospital.
