OL,6,FThe man was then hit over the head 46
OL,7,Ftimes, with Saleem responsible for 20
OL,8,Fblows and Owa 26.
OL,10,FThe victim reported the assault to the
OL,11,Fpolice after being discharged.
OL,13,FHe said he remembered being beaten but
OL,14,Fcould not identify the perpetrators
OL,15,Fdue to his state that night. The
OL,16,Fdetails of the attack was revealed
OL,17,Fonce hospital bosses accessed the
OL,18,Ffootage taken by the body worn cameras.
