OL,6,FThe attackers were 'concerned' the
OL,7,Fincident would be caught on camera,
OL,8,Fbut their efforts to turn the cameras
OL,9,Foff failed.
OL,11,FSaleem and Owa pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fassault occasioning actual bodily
OL,13,Fharm, and Monese to common assault.JIn
OL,14,Fa statement read on his behalf, the
OL,15,Fvictim said: "I was taken to hospital
OL,16,Fbecause I had taken an overdose
OL,17,Fbecause I wanted to kill myself."
