OL,6,FThe court heard Saleem had been
OL,7,Fpromoted to supervisor five months
OL,8,Fbefore the incident, while also having
OL,9,Fa baby at the time. She said Saleem is
OL,10,Fthe 'sole breadwinner' for his wife
OL,11,Fand child as well as his parents and
OL,12,Fseven siblings, who all live in a
OL,13,Fthree-bedroom house.JDefending Owa,
OL,14,FStephen Ferns said the defendant, a
OL,15,Fgrandfather, was 'shocked and
OL,16,Fhorrified at his own actions' after
OL,17,Fseeing the footage of the attack. He
OL,18,Fsubmitted a letter of apology to the
OL,19,Fvictim expressing how he is 'extremely
OL,20,Fsorry for what has happened'.J"He did
OL,21,Fthis job because he loved doing it...
OL,22,FHe considered up to this point he had
OL,23,Fbeen helping people, he had been
OL,24,Fmaking a difference.J"As a result of
OL,25,Fhis actions on the day he did
OL,26,Fcompletely the opposite."
