OL,6,FThe two men were handed 18-month
OL,7,Fcommunity orders, and ordered to
OL,8,Fcomplete 250 hours of unpaid work and
OL,9,Frehabilitation activity requirement
OL,10,Fdays with the probation service.JBoth
OL,11,Fwere also told to observe a curfew
OL,12,Ffrom 8pm to 6am for four months, and
OL,13,Fboth were ordered to pay the victim
OL,14,F#500 in compensation.JMonese was
OL,15,Fpreviously sentenced to a 12-month
OL,16,Fcommunity order by magistrates, who
OL,17,Falso ordered him to carry out 80 hours
OL,18,Fof unpaid work and rehabilitation
OL,19,Factivity.JAfter the hearing, Samira
OL,20,FChoudhry, Senior Crown Prosecutor for
OL,21,FCPS North West, said: "Abdul Saleem,
OL,22,FOwa Darling and Benjamin Monese were
OL,23,Femployed by the hospital to keep
OL,24,Fstaff, patients and visitors safe.
